fields.name: Espresso
fields.description: A strong, concentrated coffee made by forcing steam through finely-ground coffee beans.
fields.flavor_notes: Bold and intense flavor with a hint of sweetness.

fields.name: Cappuccino
fields.description: A classic Italian coffee drink made with equal parts espresso, steamed milk, and frothed milk.

fields.name: Latte
fields.description: A coffee drink made with espresso and steamed milk.
fields.flavor_notes: Smooth and creamy with a hint of espresso.

fields.name: Mocha
fields.description: A coffee drink made with espresso, chocolate, and steamed milk.
fields.flavor_notes: Rich chocolate flavor with a hint of coffee.

fields.name: Americano
fields.description: A coffee drink made by diluting espresso with hot water.
fields.flavor_notes: Bold and slightly bitter flavor with a smooth finish.

fields.name: Flat White
fields.description: A coffee drink made with espresso and microfoam.
fields.flavor_notes: Creamy texture with a strong espresso flavor.

fields.name: Macchiato
fields.description: A coffee drink made with espresso and a small amount of steamed milk.
fields.flavor_notes: Strong espresso flavor with a touch of sweetness from the milk.

fields.name: Affogato
fields.description: A dessert coffee made with a scoop of vanilla ice cream topped with a shot of espresso.
fields.flavor_notes: Creamy and decadent with a strong espresso kick.

fields.name: Turkish Coffee
fields.description: A traditional method of preparing coffee using very finely ground coffee beans boiled with water and sugar.
fields.flavor_notes: Rich and full-bodied with a thick texture.

fields.name: Irish Coffee
fields.description: A cocktail consisting of hot coffee, Irish whiskey, and sugar, stirred, and topped with cream.
fields.flavor_notes: Warm and comforting with a kick of whiskey.

fields.name: Iced Coffee
fields.description: Chilled coffee served over ice cubes.
fields.flavor_notes: Refreshing and cool with a smooth flavor.

fields.name: Vietnamese Iced Coffee
fields.description: Strong brewed coffee mixed with sweetened condensed milk and served over ice.
fields.flavor_notes: Sweet and creamy with a bold coffee flavor.

fields.name: Ristretto
fields.description: An espresso shot with less water, resulting in a more concentrated and intense flavor.
fields.flavor_notes: Rich and bold flavor with a smooth finish.
